name: Cosmos of the Mind
description:
Everything the human mind can conceive or perceive is reflected on the Tapestry.
Hope and despair, dreams and nightmares, joy and pain, prosperity and tragedy; everything has its counterpart there. The more minds that share the same feeling or idea, the stronger it becomes.
At times when humanity is united in thought, these reflections can become powerful enough to drastically change the shape of the realm of realms, for good or ill.
